        public void execute(boolean immediate,
                    String args)
             throws IOException
        Execute the APP
        Parameters:
        immediate - immediate execute or not
        if not, execute after the current APP exits
        args - execute args string
        multiple parameters are separated by a space character
        for example: arg1 arg2 ...
        Throws:
        IOException - If an I/O error occurs
